{"id": 2203, "genre": 1001, "title": "关于“紧凑型家居”，你都有哪些设想？", "description": "哪些东西可以做减法，怎样高效利用空间？（题图来自：Pixabay）", "record_count": 1212, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20180301171005ZNomxLwgAWtaflyn.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 2, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2018-03-02T03:00:00Z", "options": [{"id": 268297, "content": "一进门啥都没有，可以随便从墙壁上，地上拉出来。。。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 974576}, {"id": 268301, "content": "买个大房子", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 844634}, {"id": 268304, "content": "舒服。", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1276266}, {"id": 268306, "content": "穷说得清新", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 596413}, {"id": 268307, "content": "模块化家具", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1272307}, {"id": 268320, "content": "紧凑的流行完全是因为……大家都没空间……", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 150304}, {"id": 268322, "content": "采用折叠式多功能家具", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1276539}, {"id": 277283, "content": "收纳功能很重要", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1324221}, {"id": 268590, "content": "HK筒子楼最紧凑", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 827344}, {"id": 269111, "content": "客厅和卫生间一定要大", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1280431}, {"id": 268089, "content": "少做顶天立地的储物空间，紧凑户型更容易压抑，多用矮柜营造通透感。", "image": null, "praise_count": 54, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1021938}, {"id": 268090, "content": "不喜欢紧凑", "image": null, "praise_count": 130, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 886822}, {"id": 268091, "content": "简单的收纳最好不是个单独功能，而是和床，墙，沙发什么的结合在一起。", "image": null, "praise_count": 20, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 886822}, {"id": 268092, "content": "减少需求，而不是整合它", "image": null, "praise_count": 51, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 149075}, {"id": 268093, "content": "简易吧台型餐桌，互联网化时代无需电视，选用榻榻米代替床，开放式厨房，存储型沙发等！", "image": null, "praise_count": 124, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1274998}, {"id": 268349, "content": "卫生间的干湿分离尤其重要，即便是十分紧凑，也不愿意最能释放压力的洗浴部分被人忽略，北京，请你反思一下。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1238066}, {"id": 268350, "content": "为什么要紧凑型家具？", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1263908}, {"id": 268097, "content": "把积灰的地方都利用起来就是了", "image": null, "praise_count": 10, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1061312}, {"id": 268098, "content": "超强收纳", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 252535}, {"id": 268354, "content": "整个房间都榻榻米，铺盖边边放画具，画具边边是零食，零食边边是电脑，电脑变边边是铺盖！环绕生活", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 853433}, {"id": 268100, "content": "让里面的东西越少就越宽敞", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1275009}, {"id": 268101, "content": "如无必要，勿添实体，做道系青年。", "image": null, "praise_count": 19, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 479517}, {"id": 268102, "content": "超过一个月没用的东西全部扔掉", "image": null, "praise_count": 28, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1039682}, {"id": 268105, "content": "书桌和外露的各种电线是房间乱糟糟的头号功臣", "image": null, "praise_count": 33, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1205949}, {"id": 268106, "content": "东西越少越好，蔬菜水果少买勤买", "image": null, "praise_count": 15, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 679778}, {"id": 268109, "content": "上床下桌最紧凑", "image": null, "praise_count": 64, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1196749}, {"id": 268110, "content": "卖了换大房子", "image": null, "praise_count": 22, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 741469}, {"id": 268111, "content": "源来如此，世界如此美好", "image": "img/option/option/201803021210176Ih3U7anL5cGY1rS.jpg", "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1275037}, {"id": 268113, "content": "面积不重要。功能齐全，划分明确，日照充足，配套完善。", "image": null, "praise_count": 42, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1156386}, {"id": 268114, "content": "床下储物柜 下陷式客厅，旁边摆书啥的 不要墙要柜子一样的墙", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 260775}, {"id": 268115, "content": "放弃选择过于笨重的茶几和餐桌", "image": null, "praise_count": 34, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1264344}, {"id": 268116, "content": "少买家具 垂直收纳", "image": null, "praise_count": 9, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 651076}, {"id": 268117, "content": "阁楼必须要啊，还有壁柜", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1275068}, {"id": 268118, "content": "充气浴缸；吊在天花板上可以降下的床；洗脸台和厨房水槽合并", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 668809}, {"id": 268119, "content": "模块化家具，提供多种收纳方式的可能。", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 101880}, {"id": 268375, "content": "紧凑有安全感", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1277004}, {"id": 268122, "content": "改变生活习惯", "image": null, "praise_count": 9, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1075138}, {"id": 268379, "content": "多功能家具，软隔断，有效率的收纳", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 107477}, {"id": 268124, "content": "橱体床，拉开睡觉，推上是橱子，家里来客人空间大，不叠被子也没人看得见", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1270345}, {"id": 268381, "content": "选择自己真正需要的，而不是一味地追求好看的", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1276663}, {"id": 268637, "content": "家具一分钱一分货 不要贪图小便宜", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1119168}, {"id": 268126, "content": "还是想住大一点的房子。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 755738}, {"id": 268128, "content": "断 舍 离", "image": null, "praise_count": 19, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 136947}, {"id": 268130, "content": "少屯便宜货", "image": null, "praise_count": 14, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1271582}, {"id": 268386, "content": "收纳空间一定要大且方便", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1141779}, {"id": 268646, "content": "配用智能家居把空间问题合理解决是未来房屋装修发展趋势，简洁高效又舒服", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1278501}, {"id": 268647, "content": "大多家具和电器方便收纳或者可以折叠", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1278487}, {"id": 268137, "content": "很多柜子", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 984098}, {"id": 268149, "content": "懂得收纳之后，家里会看起来很舒服！紧凑也有收纳的智慧！", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1273319}, {"id": 268155, "content": "卧室浓缩为一张床，客厅用写字台工作区代替，地面抬高作为储存，厨房开放", "image": null, "praise_count": 12, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 926725}]}